content: **"The captain of the team, a tall, handsome, blue-eyed blonde. This is Professor Lytkin from the future. He is wearing beautiful combat glasses, shimmering with all the colors of the rainbow. He is standing on the bridge of a snow-white ocean liner. Next to him is his wife, a tall young plump blonde. The wife has big bright blue eyes, full lips, short cropped hair. She is dressed in beautiful light summer clothes. Next to his wife is her daughter, exactly like her mother. On the deck of the ship, we also see the captain's past family, consisting of an ex-wife and four sons. The ex-wife has brown eyes, dark hair, she is small. The eldest son looks like his dad, he is a software engineer. The second son is a judge, in a black robe and a white shirt. The third son is a matemtatic, smiling, curly-haired. The fourth son looks like a dad in his youth. Everyone is dressed in beautiful light summer clothes.
